      • createSchemaForEdit

        public static org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.model.api.DataNodeContainer createSchemaForEdit(org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.model.api.SchemaContext schemaContext)
        Creates artificial schema node for edit-config rpc. This artificial schema looks like: 
         rpc
   edit-config
     config
         // All schema nodes from remote schema
     config
   edit-config
 rpc
        This makes the translation of rpc edit-config request(especially the config node) to xml use schema which is crucial for some types of nodes e.g. identity-ref.

      • createSchemaForGet

 rpc
